name: tango*

name: a mother's love
description:
i specially made this to remember the recent passing of my late grandmother. she was a strong-willed woman who was full of love for her children and grandchildren, someone who was beautiful both inside and out, and extremely tough within. a mother’s love is brimming with beauty and love. the rose quartz is the perfect colour of baby pink, showing its delicacy and yet being hard as rock. it’s an intricate and extremely gorgeous piece made out of a range of crystals and semi-precious stones.
this exclusive necklace features: * 925 silver plated thin chain * finished with flower toggle clasp * genuine rose quartz carved into a flower as the centrepiece * genuine pink coral
  • mint swarovski crystals
  • genuine rose quartz briolettes
  • plastic green leaves
item will arrive packaged in an exclusive black velvet pouch

name: princess jasmine*
description:
whenever i think of princess jasmine from aladdin, for some reason, purple always comes to mind. it’s jewel-toned gorgeousness packed in one little accessory. what’s more, it’s the colour of the season!

name: out tonight*
description:
perfect for a dinner but make sure that you don’t get your pasta necklace next to the fire or it might just cook (and beware, it will not be edible!) truth be told, it is a real pasta but it’s been treated so that it’ll stay hard and not break. make sure you do take good care of it though, for it is still rather fragile due to its nature!
this necklace features: * jet black thick circular chain * genuine oval olive jade
